sentence: what are the states that border the state with the greatest population ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the states that border the state with the greatest population ?
sql: select border_info.state_name from state , border_info where state.state_name = border_info.border and state.population = ( select max ( state.population ) from state ) ;
sql-with-vars: select border_info.state_name from state , border_info where state.state_name = border_info.border and state.population = ( select max ( state.population ) from state ) ;
